{"tid":1805180,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[投票] 好老實講熱狗係咪手足","createTime":"2019-12-31T12:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T13:29:55.000Z","uid":251732,"like":70,"dislike":437,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"76dd803dccabf3803a9da967b6e7d80eac0d92a5","tid":1805180,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"我冇辦法對呢啲人渣有嘢講， 但係我想問下佢哋呢啲咁嘅人渣係咪我哋嘅手足？<br />\n由始至終佢哋對我哋嘅評價根本就係冷嘲熱諷，甚至鞭撻！<br />\n特別係嗰個仆街熱血時報根本就係一個自吹自擂嘅乞衣網媒<br />\n所以不如喺 2019年最後一個鐘頭評價下呢班極具爭議性嘅跳樑小丑， 起碼都睇下我哋呢個蓮燈係咪歡迎佢哋嘅存在<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 雖然佢仆街係咁㗎啦 但起碼都係喺背後默默支持手足 </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong> 冷嘲熱諷不特止仲要對我哋嘅手足落井下石 人格低劣過共產黨</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7c380f530e48756640890cd649cd3c06d35672f3","tid":1805180,"uid":20820,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"你唔提都差d唔記得佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2089440ea7101d2f9337ecab1802b1a7ce94513","tid":1805180,"uid":251732,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7c380f530e48756640890cd649cd3c06d35672f3","tid":1805180,"uid":20820,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"你唔提都差d唔記得佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T12:58:39.000Z","msg":"咁始終呢度咁多第一次參與社運嘅手足<br />\n 起碼都要畀佢哋知道過去嘅歷史係點樣走"},{"pid":"9b5f3fb84f9babcc9521f2d40059070d5ef95f9e","tid":1805180,"uid":48083,"like":19,"dislike":4,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:00:12.000Z","msg":"討論完有乜野意義？<br />\n同分黃藍一樣<br />\n自己google, 用吓個閪腦諗<br />\n想撐就撐想反就反<br />\n唔撚使&lsquo;公論&rsquo;"},{"pid":"c47cac94ae2b471bbf0f69239a452b3310b1439f","tid":1805180,"uid":179409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"自己上網搵下<br />\n退咗熱